description: This file is a React application entry point that sets up rendering of the main App component into the DOM element with id 'root'. It imports React, ReactDOM, a CSS file, and the App component, then renders the App within React.StrictMode for development safety.

methods.name: createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root React DOM node for rendering the React application.

methods.name: render
methods.description: Renders the React React element tree into the root DOM node.
